            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-pink-600 mb-2">Valentine's Day</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Romantic, sweet, and playful cards to share the love on Valentine's Day with someone special.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl border border-green-100 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="img-zoom aspect-[16/10]">
