          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-green-600 mb-2">Easter</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Cheerful Easter cards with springtime charm, bunnies, blooms, and messages of renewal and joy.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl border border-pink-100 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="img-zoom aspect-[16/10]">
            <img src="<%= siteImage('greeting-cards.mothers-day') %>" alt="Mother's Day cards" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
