        </article>

        <article class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl border border-blue-100 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="img-zoom aspect-[16/10]">
            <img src="<%= siteImage('greeting-cards.fathers-day') %>" alt="Father's Day cards" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-blue mb-2">Father's Day</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Cards to celebrate dads, grandpas, and father figures with humor, warmth, and appreciation.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl border border-orange-100 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="img-zoom aspect-[16/10]">
            <img src="<%= siteImage('greeting-cards.halloween') %>" alt="Halloween cards" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-orange mb-2">Halloween</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Spooky and fun Halloween cards for trick-or-treat season, costume parties, and haunted celebrations.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl border border-amber-100 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="img-zoom aspect-[16/10]">
            <img src="<%= siteImage('greeting-cards.thanksgiving') %>" alt="Thanksgiving cards" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-amber-700 mb-2">Thanksgiving</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Give thanks with warm and grateful Thanksgiving cards for gatherings, hosts, and loved ones.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl border border-blue-100 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="img-zoom aspect-[16/10]">
            <img src="<%= siteImage('greeting-cards.hanukkah') %>" alt="Hanukkah cards" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-brand-blue mb-2">Hanukkah</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Celebrate the Festival of Lights with beautiful Hanukkah cards featuring menorahs and seasonal warmth.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="category-card bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md hover:shadow-xl border border-purple-100 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="img-zoom aspect-[16/10]">
            <img src="<%= siteImage('greeting-cards.new-year') %>" alt="New Year cards" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-purple-600 mb-2">New Year</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ring in the new year with festive celebration cards full of hope, sparkle, and fresh beginnings.</p>
